  <brief_title>Safety, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of LGT209 in Healthy Volunteers With Elevated Cholesterol and in Hypercholesterolemic Patients Treated With Statins</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Single Dose, Parallel Group Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, Bioavailability, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of Subcutaneous LGT209 in Hypercholesterolemic Patients on Stable Doses of Atorvastatin or Simvastatin and in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
