  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to investigate the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics and
      pharmacodynamics of LGT209 in hypercholesterolemic patients taking common statin medications
      and in healthy volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
